---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Marketing Company Edinburgh" description="Our commitment to your privacy and how we handle data for our Edinburgh marketing clients.">
	<section class="py-32 bg-slate-50">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none 
				prose-headings:text-[#0A192F] prose-headings:font-black 
				prose-p:text-gray-600 prose-p:leading-relaxed 
				prose-strong:text-[#0A192F]">
				<p>Last Updated: April 9, 2026</p>
				<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
				<p>At Marketing Company Edinburgh, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data in compliance with UK GDPR and other relevant regulations.</p>
				<h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
				<p>We collect information you provide directly to us via our contact forms, such as your name, email, and website URL. We also use analytics to improve our website's performance and user experience.</p>
				<h2>3. Use of Information</h2>
				<p>Your data is used solely to provide and improve our marketing services, communicate with you about your projects, and send you our "Edinburgh Marketing Insights" newsletter if you have opted in.</p>
				<h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
				<p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data at any time. Please contact us at info@marketing-company.co.uk for any privacy-related requests.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
